{"tid":1780941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【教育已死】做緊補習社 對住啲深藍小學生好絕望","createTime":"2019-12-12T19:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T07:10:58.000Z","uid":264736,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"676e5b5ecb5f510f68d07326c76d4449ad1d3632","tid":1780941,"uid":264736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T19:09:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">呢區明明都黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />附近都係文宣黃店⋯⋯<br />\n但係啲小朋友中文造句作文鍾意講：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「廢青暴徒積極投放汽油彈」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「香港是個充滿曱甴的混亂社會」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「警察見義勇為，捨己救人，保護市民」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「暴徒見人就打」之類⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我知佢哋接受資訊淨係得tvb 爸爸媽媽，<br />\n學校永遠教佢哋有規矩就要守，仲有大把呃飯「老師」，依家講多啲其他嘢都要驚住被投訴，取消教師資格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地仲係小學生/初中，我又唔係好知應該點同佢哋解釋，但次次聽到都好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過幾年取消粵語教中文，取消聆聽說話卷，取消通識，加維穩中史，國民教育⋯⋯第時會點，我真係諗都唔敢諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日日對住佢哋心都寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"23ebb1870df150213f080fa920e7672e0ca428f3","tid":1780941,"uid":277186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T19:12:54.000Z","msg":"成日聽到堆小學生講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c47d6df5067a4c3d68f48762099125e1497fc4","tid":1780941,"uid":64487,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T19:12:57.000Z","msg":"所以要靠你教翻好佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceccb1295ce6